OL,6,FMr Cooke told the newspaper: "None of
OL,7,Fthe organisations can hold their head
OL,8,Fup high and say: 'We're doing all we
OL,9,Fcan'. The entire criminal justice
OL,10,Fsystem is dysfunctional, undoubtedly
OL,11,Fdysfunctional."
OL,13,FHis comments come amid growing
OL,14,Fconcerns over the capacity of prisons,
OL,15,Fwith the Government introducing an
OL,16,Fearly release scheme which will see
OL,17,Fthousands of prisoners released after
OL,18,Fserving 40% of their sentence.
