OL,6,FThe prison population of England and
OL,7,FWales hit a record high earlier this
OL,8,Fweek, with 88,350 people in prison as
OL,9,Fof August 30, according to the
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice.
OL,12,FAn estimated 5,500 offenders are
OL,13,Fexpected to be released earlier than
OL,14,Fwas planned in the coming weeks under
OL,15,Fthe Government's temporary measures to
OL,16,Fease overcrowding.
OL,18,FThe scheme will not apply to those
OL,19,Fconvicted of sex offences, terrorism,
OL,20,Fdomestic abuse or some violent
OL,21,Foffences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
