OL,6,FSpeaking to journalists while on a
OL,7,Ftrip to Berlin earlier this week, Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer said that more prisons
OL,9,Fwill be built in response to
OL,10,Fovercrowding once the Government has
OL,11,Fgot its "hands on the planning laws".
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, the Prime Minister said:
OL,14,F"We've got to change the planning
OL,15,Fregulation so we can build the prisons
OL,16,Fwe need, because they're taking far
OL,17,Ftoo long, it's far too slow, and
OL,18,Fthat's amongst the reasons we're in
OL,19,Fthe position we are.
OL,26,@sD@IOUsD@dO]vD@AOU
