OL,4,Cjustice system 'dysfunctional'
OL,6,F"And, as you'd expect from an ex-chief
OL,7,Fprosecutor, people do need to go to
OL,8,Fprison, and they need to know that the
OL,9,Flaw is effective."
OL,11,FHe added: "We need to build those
OL,12,Fprisons, and we will get our hands on
OL,13,Fthe planning laws in order to do so."
OL,15,FMr Cooke told the Telegraph while
OL,16,Fofficers cannot respond to everything
OL,17,Freported, victims' needs should still
OL,18,Fbe at the heart of every job.
