OL,6,F"It is difficult to try and balance
OL,7,Fyour resources, but you can't forget
OL,8,Fwhat's important to the public that
OL,9,Fyou serve," he said.
OL,11,FMr Cooke also pledged to continue
OL,12,Fcalling for the Royal Commission into
OL,13,Fcriminal justice, which was promised
OL,14,Fin 2019 but is yet to materialise.
OL,16,FIn addition to extra work placed on
OL,17,Fpolice, he said, said there were also
OL,18,Fissues with the way funding was
OL,19,Fallocated across the UK.
